# private online portfolio builder 

## The idea for this web service is to give users the tools to create a simple online portfolio which would allow them to fill in online portfolio sections in job searches without the need to use wordpress and other web services to set one up. This tool uses simple prompts for the user to imput their CV as a pdf as well as youtube chanel links github links and others as well as changing the colour of the background and putting a welcome messege. This allows users to temporarily upload their past works relating to their carrer aspirations but only in the time period where they are looking for work.
